  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will compare two strategies for bowel cleansing prior to inpatient colonoscopy:
      the entire preparation taken the night before the procedure versus half the preparation
      taken the night before the procedure, and the other half taken the morning of the procedure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
